= JetPack =
The NVIDIA JetPack SDK is a installer to flash the Jetson Developer Kit with the latest OS image, install developer tools for the host PC and Developer Kit and to install libraries, APIs, samples and documentations needed to start with your development environment. Further information about the installation: [[https:~~/~~/docs.nvidia.com/jetson/jetpack/index.html>>url:https://docs.nvidia.com/jetson/jetpack/index.html]]
